The paper discusses computer vision systems and machine learning approaches for interpreting videos from unconstrained mobility platforms like UAVs. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of supervised machine learning approaches, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses image restoration and enhancement algorithms, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper mentions the UG^2 dataset, which is related to ground robotics (cs.GR).
